  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libvirt-glib</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libvirt-glib</application> package wraps libvirt
      to provide a high-level object-oriented API better suited for
      glib-based applications.
    </para>

    &lfs71_checked;

